25/03/2009
TIRANA, Albania -- Police arrested a 35-year-old man Tuesday (March 24th) suspected of killing two policemen a day earlier. The arrest in the northern town of Kukes followed a massive manhunt. Police believe the suspect murdered the officers because they prevented him from constructing an illegal building. (Shekulli, Balkan Web, Telegrafi, Top Channel - 24/03/09) 
